    <title>Week 9 Qui<m>\scalebox{-1}[1]{z}</m></title>

    <p>Suppose that <m>f \in \mathcal{R}[0,1]</m>. Compute <md number="yes" xml:id="limit-integral9">\lim_{n \to \infty} \int_0^1 f(x) x^n dx</md>.</p>

    <p>
        Note that this is the same as in <xref ref="limit-integral9"/>
